OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F449A1775589083
OL,3,CChild hit by bottle and nine police
OL,4,Cofficers injured before football match
OL,6,FA 19-year-old man has been arrested
OL,7,Ffollowing disorder which took place
OL,8,Fbefore the Irish Cup semi-final match
OL,9,Fin Belfast.
OL,11,FPolice said a child was hit by a
OL,12,Fbottle and nine officers were injured
OL,13,Fas fireworks, flares and bottles were
OL,14,Fthrown in the scenes at Windsor Park
OL,15,Fon Friday evening.
OL,17,FIt came before the match between north
OL,18,FBelfast side Cliftonville and
OL,19,FDungannon Swifts.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/7
