PN,44902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F449A1775589083
OL,3,CChild hit by bottle and nine police
OL,4,Cofficers injured before football match
OL,6,FA number of Cliftonville supporters
OL,7,Fhad taken part in a parade ahead of
OL,8,Fthe clash, which Swifts won on
OL,9,Fpenalties after a 1-1 draw.
OL,11,FSouth Belfast district commander
OL,12,FSuperintendent Finola Dornan said
OL,13,Fduring the procession "provocative
OL,14,Fconduct" and "heavy use of
OL,15,Fpyrotechnics and fireworks" was
OL,16,Fobserved.
OL,18,FShe said a 19-year-old was arrested on
OL,19,Fsuspicion of riotous behaviour and two
OL,20,Fwere reported for offences including
OL,21,Fthe use of flares.
OL,26,@uD@WOUvD@HO]vD@NOUwD@[O]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/7
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,450,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F449A1775589083
OL,3,CChild hit by bottle and nine police
OL,4,Cofficers injured before football match
OL,6,F"While the majority of football fans
OL,7,Fattending Friday evening's match
OL,8,Fbehaved in a peaceful manner, a number
OL,9,Fof people chose to engage in
OL,10,Fdisorderly behaviour and provocative
OL,11,Fconduct," she said.
OL,13,F"During an approved public procession
OL,14,Fahead of the match, which involved
OL,15,Fapproximately 250 people, our officers
OL,16,Fwitnessed provocative conduct and the
OL,17,Fheavy use of pyrotechnics and
OL,18,Ffireworks ` despite various warnings
OL,19,Fbeing issued against this."
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@IO]uD@AOU{D@[O]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/7
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,450,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F449A1775589083
OL,3,CChild hit by bottle and nine police
OL,4,Cofficers injured before football match
OL,6,FShe said there appeared to be a number
OL,7,Fof potential breaches of the Parades
OL,8,FCommission determinations in relation
OL,9,Fto the procession which will be
OL,10,Finvestigated.
OL,12,F"A 19-year-old man was arrested on
OL,13,Fsuspicion of riotous behaviour, doing
OL,14,Fa provocative act, possession of
OL,15,Ffireworks/flares at a regulated match,
OL,16,Findecent behaviour and attempted
OL,17,Fcriminal damage. He remains in police
OL,18,Fcustody at this time," she said.
OL,26,@tD@AOUzD@VO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/7
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,450,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F449A1775589083
OL,3,CChild hit by bottle and nine police
OL,4,Cofficers injured before football match
OL,6,F"Two other people were also reported
OL,7,Ffor offences including the use of
OL,8,Fflares."
OL,10,FShe added: "The vast majority of fans
OL,11,Fwere there to enjoy the match, however
OL,12,Fthere was completely unacceptable
OL,13,Fbehaviour from a proportion of fans
OL,14,Fboth before and after the match, at
OL,15,Fwhat should have been an enjoyable and
OL,16,Fsafe event for all attending.
OL,26,@nD@AOUpD@HO]rD@LOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G5/7
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,450,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44906
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F449A1775589083
OL,3,CChild hit by bottle and nine police
OL,4,Cofficers injured before football match
OL,6,F"Police will not tolerate disorder or
OL,7,Fcriminal behaviour of any kind and, as
OL,8,Falways, we will continue to work with
OL,9,Ffootball clubs to address any
OL,10,Finappropriate behaviour linked to
OL,11,Fpeople attending matches and ensure
OL,12,Fthat the local community is kept safe.
OL,14,F"We will therefore be conducting a
OL,15,Fthorough evidence-gathering operation
OL,16,Fin the wake of last night's
OL,17,Foccurrences."
OL,19,FCatch up with the latest UTV Live on
OL,20,FITVX
